  "detailed_description": "The brand new helicopter game from independent developers Bohemia Interactive – creators of the award-winning military-Sim series Arma 2. Built upon over 10 years of experience in cutting-edge simulator development, Take On Helicopters immerses players within beautifully rich landscapes and an authentic flight model.<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe player takes on the role of a civilian helicopter pilot. Harry Larkin’s aviation business has fallen on tough times. Built up over decades, it’s now only days away from closure. His sons face an uncertain future, struggling to save the company their father spent his whole life building. Together, they must take on contracts and competitors; together, they take on helicopters!<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTake your first steps towards mastering rotor-wing flight across a massive range of enjoyable challenges, or create your own missions using the powerful easy-to-use mission editor.<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTake to the air above two beautifully rich and expansive environments, based upon real-world North American and South Asian terrain-data.<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTake on cutting-edge technology, helicopters modeled in stunning detail, a large-scale, open-world sandbox and authentic flight dynamics…<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take On Helicopters Offers:</h2>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>High fidelity flight dynamics modelling<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Richly modelled helicopters & cockpits<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Expansive & detailed environments<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Powerful & intuitive mission editor<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Multiplayer – co-op & competitive scenarios<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take On Helicopters features two huge terrains:</h2>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Seattle</strong>, a 60x60km chunk of North America <br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li><strong>South Asia</strong>, a 120x120km terrain populated with vegetation and urban structures.<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take On Helicopters introduces the player to three distinct classes of helicopter:</h2>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/65730/extras/LIGHT_thumb_308x140.png\" /></span><strong>Light</strong></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/65730/extras/MEDIUM_thumb_308x140.png\" /></span></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/65730/extras/HEAVY_thumb_308x140.png\" /></span></ul></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "The brand new helicopter game from independent developers Bohemia Interactive – creators of the award-winning military-Sim series Arma 2. Built upon over 10 years of experience in cutting-edge simulator development, Take On Helicopters immerses players within beautifully rich landscapes and an authentic flight model.<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe player takes on the role of a civilian helicopter pilot. Harry Larkin’s aviation business has fallen on tough times. Built up over decades, it’s now only days away from closure. His sons face an uncertain future, struggling to save the company their father spent his whole life building. Together, they must take on contracts and competitors; together, they take on helicopters!<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTake your first steps towards mastering rotor-wing flight across a massive range of enjoyable challenges, or create your own missions using the powerful easy-to-use mission editor.<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTake to the air above two beautifully rich and expansive environments, based upon real-world North American and South Asian terrain-data.<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTake on cutting-edge technology, helicopters modeled in stunning detail, a large-scale, open-world sandbox and authentic flight dynamics…<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take On Helicopters Offers:</h2>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>High fidelity flight dynamics modelling<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Richly modelled helicopters & cockpits<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Expansive & detailed environments<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Powerful & intuitive mission editor<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Multiplayer – co-op & competitive scenarios<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take On Helicopters features two huge terrains:</h2>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Seattle</strong>, a 60x60km chunk of North America <br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li><strong>South Asia</strong>, a 120x120km terrain populated with vegetation and urban structures.<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take On Helicopters introduces the player to three distinct classes of helicopter:</h2>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/65730/extras/LIGHT_thumb_308x140.png\" /></span><strong>Light</strong></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/65730/extras/MEDIUM_thumb_308x140.png\" /></span></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/65730/extras/HEAVY_thumb_308x140.png\" /></span></ul></ul>",
